Directory Structure:
+- $HOME
 +- SASiDet/

navigate to the directory above SASiDet/ and then create a build directory

$ cd $HOME
$ mkdir SASiDet_build

Directory Structure:
+- $HOME
 +- SASiDet/
 +- SASiDet_build/

$ cd $HOME/SASiDet_build
$ cmake -DGeant4_DIR=/home/where/you/installed/Geant4 $HOME/SASiDet

Now compile:
$ make

Run in interactive mode:
$ ./SASiDet

Or run provided macro file:
$ ./SASiDet thesis_no_abs_const.mac
